Sentencas: When LSM powder is mixed with CeO2 and sintered at 1400 degrees C for 4 h, manganese aluminate spinel, MnAl2O4 and Mn2AlO4, forms at LSM/LSM, LSM/CeO2 and CeO2/CeO2 boundaries.
